headline: eHealth (EHTH) Reports Q2 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: eHealth (EHTH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -12.64% and +28.54%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
